# 👤 Face Recognition Java App (GUI + MySQL)

This Java application demonstrates a **Face Recognition system** using a **Swing GUI**, **MySQL database**, and **OOP principles**. It currently simulates face detection and stores user details in a MySQL database.

## 📌 Features

- GUI built with `Swing`
- Object-Oriented Programming (Encapsulation, Classes)
- JDBC connection to MySQL
- Simulated face detection (OpenCV integration ready)
- Input validation and exception handling

---

## 🚀 Technologies Used

- Java (JDK 8+)
- Swing (GUI)
- MySQL (via JDBC)
- JDBC Connector (`mysql-connector-java`)

---

## 🧑‍💻 How to Run

### 1. 📦 Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/face-recognition-java.git
cd face-recognition-java
